headline.main: BUNDLE' CONCERT BRINGS 1,000 GIFTS; Donors Admitted to Carnegie Hall in Drive for Million Packages for British

lead_paragraph: Three ambulance-loads of bundles were collected yesterday morning at a concert in Carnegie Hall to which no one was admitted unless he or she first left some contribution for the British people at one of the receiving stations in the lobby.
abstract: Bundles for Brit and Music Clubs Natl Fed sponsor concert, N Y C; Mrs W Latham thanks audience for gifts; Brit-Amer Ambulance Corps and Amer Musicians Fed benefit concert, N Y C
